The package provides several fonts: Croatian Glagolitic
(round—sometimes called Bulgarian Glagolitic, angular, Baška
tablet, cursive, ligatures, the Baromić broken ligatures,
calligraphic), Croatian Cyrillic, stećak ornaments and
Croatian wattle patterns. The fonts are provided as MetaFont
source; some Plain TeX macro support is provided, including
hyphenation patterns.
